00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:45,360
You sell your own compatriots for foreigners.

426
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,960
How dirty your money is!

427
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,080
Did I ask you to speak?

428
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:48,560
Liangchen.

