507
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,040
Yeah.

508
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:25,960
So I trust you.

509
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:30,820
Xie Liangchen.

510
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:34,200
